<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٨٥١ - حَدِيثٌ <span class="c2">(ط)</span> : <span class="c1">" إِذَا دَخَلَتْ فِي الْحَيْضَةِ الثَّالِثَةِ فَقَدْ بَانَتْ مِنْهُ "</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٦٥٧⦘ الْحَدِيثَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">فِي تَرْجَمَةِ:</span> عَبْدِ رَبِّهِ، عَنْ نَافِعٍ، عَنِ ابْنِ عُمَرَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>